01:38:27,858 --> 01:38:31,149
when l held you in my
hands for the first time..

712
01:38:32,358 --> 01:38:40,690
l made a promise, never to let happen
to my daughter, what happened to me

713
01:38:42,025 --> 01:38:47,565
