721
01:39:28,525 --> 01:39:33,815
Because your father
won't care for your tears

722
01:39:35,525 --> 01:39:40,149
For the happinesses of everyone,
l beg of you

723
01:39:42,191 --> 01:39:45,940
Forget him, my Child

724
01:40:03,108 --> 01:40:04,732
You're right, Ma

725
01:40:06,066 --> 01:40:13,857
